-- Phil Mickelson Wins British Open for Fifth Major Golf Title
-- B y   C h r i s t o p h e r   E l s e r
-- 2013-07-21T16:49:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-21/phil-mickelson-wins-british-open-for-fifth-major-golf-title.html
Phil Mickelson won the British Open
by three shots for his fifth major golf championship.  Mickelson shot 5-under par today to finish with a score of
3-under 281 at Muirfield in Gullane,  Scotland . The 43-year-old
American birdied four of the final six holes today on the way to
his first British Open title.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Christopher Elser in London at 
